Package graphpack.extensions.trustpack

extends GraphPack with trust management facilities

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AggregateOperator.AgrrFunc<B,C> a function which `add' a value to a given aggregation
Evaluation an evaluation contained within some trust statement
MapOperator.MapFunc<T,S> a function which maps a single value to a new value
 

Class Summary
AggregateOperator contains aggregation operators
AggregateOperator.Sum a sum aggregation
Entity wraps a node - can be a trustor or a trustee of trust statements
Evaluation.Balance stores a balance of negative an positive experience
Evaluation.Cons<T1,T2> stores two evaluations together
Evaluation.Normalized stores a evaluation that consists of a single double value
MapOperator maps values new values
TrustPack an extension which extends a graphpack node into a trustpack entity
TS a trust statement that was made from one entity to another
